        <button class="accordion">About the website</button>
        <div class="panel">
            <p>This is a unique project that aims to bring like-minded readers together and help them share, 
                borrow or exchange books without the hassle of incessant buying. It is a portal where you can 
                upload the books you would like to exchange and find the books you would like to borrow without 
                any costs.
            </p>
        </div>

        <button class="accordion">Getting started on the website</button>
        <div class="panel">
            <p>To get started you just have to follow a few simple steps. 
                Open the signup page of our website and fill in the details asked.
                Once you have signed in you will be able to access all the books available on the website.
                Go and find the book that interests you the most!
            </p>
        </div>

        <button class="accordion">Will my information be shared?</button>
        <div class="panel">
            <p>Your information is completely safe with us. 
                Only your email ID will be shared with others on our website who have signed up just like you.
                No, we will not be sharing your information to a third-party organization.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <button class="accordion">Where can I ask my queries?</button>
