            <p>You can contact us at gfg.srmist@gmail.com</p>
        </div>

        <button class="accordion">Reviewing and uploading books</button>
        <div class="panel">
            <p>You can search the books by genre and can also upload the books you would like to share with others.
                You can write reviews for the books you have read and go through otherâ€™s reviews to choose your next book.                
            </p>
        </div>

        <button class="accordion">How will the exchange take place?</button>
        <div class="panel">
            <p>The exchange is completely between you and the person whose book you've chosen to borrow. 
                We provide a platform for like-minded readers to get in touch. Further communication can take 
                place between the two people as per their comfort via the contact information provided.                
            </p>
        </div>

        <button class="accordion">When will I have to return the book?</button>
        <div class="panel">
            <p>The return will be completely based on the understanding between you and the person whose book you 
                have borrowed and the stipulated time you both have agreed upon.             
            </p>
        </div>

        <button class="accordion">Do I have to pay a registration or exchange fee?</button>
        <div class="panel">
            <p>This is a complete free portal. There is absolutely no registration charge whatsoever. It is simply a
                 platform to facilitate the exchange and borrowing of books as opposed to incessant buying.             
